
<h2> <%= contest.title %> </h2>

<% if current_user and current_user.admin? %>
<nav>
  <ul>
    <li><%= link_to "edit", edit_contest_path(contest) %></li>
    <li><%= link_to "show", contest_path(contest) %></li>
  </ul>
</nav>
<% end %>

<div class="rules">

<h2>Rules</h2>

<p>
To submit an entry, just sign up, log in, navigate to "My Home" and
click the "New Entry" button.  On the entry deadline, any entry with valid povray
code that renders an image will enter the voting gallery.  All users with at
least one entry will be able to vote for the winner.
</p>

<p><%=h contest.rules %></p>

<hr/>

<h2>Important Dates</h2>

<p>
<b><%=h contest.entrydeadline.getlocal.strftime("%A %B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z") %></b>.  Entries are due.
All entries submitted for this contest will be saved and become part of the voting gallery.
Contestants may no longer edit or delete their entries.  Entries are given some time
to render before voting begins.
</p>

<p>
<b><%=h contest.votingstart.getlocal.strftime("%A %B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z") %></b> Voting begins.
Contestents vote for their top three choices.  Contestents may not vote for their own entries.
</p>

<p>
<b><%=h contest.votingend.getlocal.strftime("%A %B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z") %></b>
Voting closes, contest results are posted.<br/>
</p>

<hr/>

<h2>Ini Files</h2>

<p>
Entries will be rendered once to create a thumbnail, and once to create a
full sized using the following ini files.
</p>

<label>Ini</label>
  <div class="code"><%=h contest.ini %></div>
<br/>

<label>Ini for Thumbnail</label>
  <div class="code"><%=h contest.thumbnailini %></div>
<br/>

</div>

<% if current_user and current_user.admin? %>
<label>Start Date<label>
  <div class="date"><%=h contest.startdate %></div>
<br/>

<label>Entry Deadline<label>
  <div class="date"><%=h contest.entrydeadline %></div>
<br/>

<label>Voting Start<label>
  <div class="date"><%=h contest.votingstart %></div>
<br/>

<label>Voting End<label>
  <div class="date"><%=h contest.votingend %></div>
<br/>
<% end %>

